She turned to see Blackstorm. "I hope you are energised. This will be a long 
trip." 

She didn't wait for a response. Acting similar to the way she was in the 
past; she opened the doors, Made sure the sentinel systems would not target 
the both of them... then made her way outside. There she trotted, leapt into 
the air, & transformed quickly & masterfully into a form that was similar to 
a jet.. roughly. 


--part1_74.2dd7b5cd.2be84f34_boundary
